 <name>Gtk2_ScrollingLabel</name>
 <channel>pear.php.net</channel>
 <summary>A Scrolling label for PHP-Gtk2</summary>
 <description>A scrolling Gtk label for PHP-Gtk2. This class provides a simple, easy to understand API for setting up and controlling the label.  It allows for the ability to scroll in either direction, start and stop the scroll, pause and unpause the scroll, get and set the text, and set display properites of the text.</description>
